                        <interp inst="t18440506-name-111" type="given" value="BENJAMIN"></interp>BENJAMIN PREW</persName>
                  </hi>. I live in Aldgate High-street. The witness brought these trowsers back to my shop—they are mine.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
