                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic">policeman.</hi>) I was coming out of a shop about seven o'clock—I heard a cry of "Stop thief"—the prisoner brushed by me, and ran up a court into a house and got behind a door—I fetched him out.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Prisoner.</hi> I was standing at the door like other people; he said he saw me chuck the trowsers over a wall. <hi rend="italic">Witness.</hi> I did not say so—I had not seen him with them—I said he might have thrown them over a wall before I knew they were found.</p>
